        <mxCell id="68" value="&lt;b&gt;Hand-Crafted Domain Features&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px;&quot;&gt;① &lt;b&gt;Peak features&lt;/b&gt; (30-d):&lt;br/&gt;   top-10 positions, heights, widths&lt;br/&gt;② &lt;b&gt;Spectral moments&lt;/b&gt; (4-d):&lt;br/&gt;   mean, std, skewness, kurtosis&lt;br/&gt;③ &lt;b&gt;Band means + ratios&lt;/b&gt; (28-d):&lt;br/&gt;   7 diagnostic windows + ⁷C₂ = 21 ratios&lt;br/&gt;④ &lt;b&gt;Subsampled spectrum&lt;/b&gt; (64-d):&lt;br/&gt;   stride-32 avg-pool from 2048→64&lt;br/&gt;⑤ &lt;b&gt;Derivative stats&lt;/b&gt; (12-d):&lt;br/&gt;   1st/2nd deriv: mean, std, max, min, ZCR, energy&lt;br/&gt;⑥ &lt;b&gt;Spectral entropy&lt;/b&gt; (1-d)&lt;br/&gt;⑦ &lt;b&gt;Band peak counts + areas&lt;/b&gt; (14-d)&lt;br/&gt;⑧ &lt;b&gt;Peak prominences&lt;/b&gt; (10-d)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Total: 163 features&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#E8F5E9;strokeColor=#2E7D32;strokeWidth=2;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;arcSize=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
